Comparison of hot and cold channel thermal performance for three configurations (1, 2, 3 layers) of the secondary lattice structures and two materials (ZrO2, Si-SiC) with radiation. For each material, also two configurations (1, 2 layers) were investigated with the presence of a constant gap between the top parting sheet and the secondary lattice structures

